TEDxGeorgiaTech - Steve Potter - NeuroEngineering: Neuroscience - Applied

Steve Potter is a Biomedical Engineering Professor at the Georgia Institute of Technology. In the spirit of ideas worth spreading, TEDx is a program of local, self-organized events that bring people together to share a TED-like experience. At a TEDx event, TEDTalks video and live speakers combine to spark deep discussion and connection in a small group.
